pull_request.title: Added signature templating code.
pull_request.body:
* Added the ability to automatically add new libOQS signature schemes to OpenSSL by specifying various algorithm data in `oqs-template/generate.yml`
* Used this to add support for the `oqsdefault` signature method and rearrange and rename the signature schemes.
